{"tid":51251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府索FB用戶資料！半年190次創新高 全涉執法問題","createTime":"2016-12-23T05:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T09:37:16.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0062cf4d6cc1a75ce506721f4f76c8c3177b389b","tid":51251,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"港府索FB用戶資料！半年190次創新高 全涉執法問題<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-23 11:27:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook最新公佈，今年上半年全球政府收集資料要求報告，其中港府要求次數達190次，不單創歷來新高，數目更比起上年全年總和184次更高；若與去年下半年113宗比較，要求次數大增68%。另外，所有要求均涉執法問題，未有一宗是就緊急求援而作出。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，自有紀錄以來，港府收集資料要求報告均持續上升。今年上半年，港府的190次收集資料要求，共涉279用戶；去年全年涉用戶總數則為415個。<br />\n<br />\n不過，今年上半年190宗要求中，只有45.79%獲Facebook正面回應；應要求而限制用戶登入內容的個案，則只有1次，行動是按衞生署控煙辦公室（控煙辦）要求作出。<br />\n<br />\n另外，全球政府首半年的要求總次數為59,229宗，較上一次公布的2015下半年的46,710宗增加27%。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=JaX4Eluyf0EPR14Lty5nzZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=02de0029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56082579&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56082579%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161223&d=JaX4Eluyf0EPR14Lty5nzZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1655059f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56082579%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161223&h=a5cffaea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56082579&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161223</a>"},{"pid":"4eb99055dfe2d900579e9e5bdc9e62849bc957a2","tid":51251,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 控煙同上fb有咩關係？"},{"pid":"a6808a033ae2ab280f2d8b93018932a8661f1918","tid":51251,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79a0a3bf20a841a0f165029cbd4a3a6175134146","tid":51251,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 控煙同上fb有咩關係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪去控煙辦fb留粗口留言? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be42d99be09f9b71dab5e9c229ab021aab01c9a","tid":51251,"uid":37281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c81ff5f9835036bbbe233213afca182cddae45e","tid":51251,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:33:37.000Z","msg":"Facebook 好講清楚邊d會俾啦"},{"pid":"bfacf8e5d2bdc9fd93506d2b38fa8313222e1bb7","tid":51251,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"美國31億次點做到"}]}